<text>
  <body>
<p>
<l rend="indent">How dare you <interp ana="#AFAM">black</interp> students of the<lb break="yes"/>
<orgName ref="#UMD">University</orgName> complain?</l></p>
<p>I think it's perfectly asinine <choice><orig>ofyou</orig><reg>of</reg></choice> you<lb break="yes"/>
people to think you can get something<lb break="yes"/>
for nothing. Furthermore, <interp ana="#PRO">I</interp> think<lb break="yes"/>
<interp ana="PRO">you've</interp> been given enough already.</p>
<p>After all, there <choice><orig>isnt</orig><reg>isn't</reg></choice> a <interp ana="#CAUC">white</interp> student<lb break="yes"/>
union on <orgName ref="#UMD">campus</orgName> <supplied>--</supplied> neither would it<lb break="yes"/>
have been permitted.</p>
<p>Look at all the money <orgName ref="#SGA">SGA</orgName> appro-<lb break="yes"/>
priated to <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> just because <choice><orig>youre</orig><reg>you're</reg></choice> <interp ana="#AFAM">black</interp>.<lb break="yes"/>
<choice><orig>Lets</orig><reg>Let's</reg></choice> face it. You <interp ana="#ASLUR">niggers</interp> get all the<lb break="yes"/>
breaks. When there's an opening in<lb break="yes"/>
the <orgName ref="#UMD">dining halls</orgName>the janitorial<lb break="yes"/>
staff, who gets the job? A <interp ana="#ASLUR">nigger</interp>.</p>
<p>Look at <affiliation><interp ana="AFAM">the riots</interp></affiliation>. You <interp ana="#ASLUR">niggers</interp><lb break="yes"/>
damned near robbed my brother-in-<lb break="yes"/>
law blind. Now he <choice><orig>cant</orig><reg>can't</reg></choice> even get<lb break="yes"/>
the <orgName>insurance company</orgName> to pay off.<lb break="yes"/>
<affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">Violence</interp></affiliation> <choice><orig>isnt</orig><reg>isn't</reg></choice> the answer especially<lb break="yes"/>
when <choice><orig>its</orig><reg>it's</reg></choice> <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">communist</interp></affiliation> inspired.</p>
<p>What if <interp ana="#PRO">we</interp> <interp ana="#CAUC">whites</interp> had armed our-<lb break="yes"/>
selves and <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">looted</interp></affiliation> <interp ana="#AFAM">black</interp> <orgName>businesses</orgName>?<lb break="yes"/>
<interp ana="#PRO">You</interp> claim that the <interp ana="#AFAM">black</interp> student<lb break="yes"/>
<interp ana="#AFAM">population</interp> <choice><orig>isnt</orig><reg>isn't</reg></choice> <affiliation>representative of<lb break="yes"/>
the <interp ana="#AFAM">black population</interp> on a whole</affiliation>.</p>
<p>Can <interp ana="#CAUC">we</interp> help it if <interp ana="#ASLUR">niggers</interp> <choice><orig>dont</orig><reg>don't</reg></choice> want<lb break="yes"/>
to come <orgName ref="#UMD">here</orgName>? Besides, nobody had<lb break="yes"/>
to tell <interp ana="#CAUC">me</interp> to come <orgName ref="#UMD">here</orgName>.</p>
<p>Furthermore, <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> have to accept<lb break="yes"/>
the fact that the <interp ana="#AFAM">black students</interp> <choice><orig>arent</orig><reg>aren't</reg></choice><lb break="yes"/>
as <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">intelligent</interp></affiliation> as <interp ana="#CAUC">whites</interp> and <affiliation>therefore<lb break="yes"/>
<interp ana="#AFAM">won't do as well in college</interp></affiliation>.</p>
<p><interp ana="#PRO">You</interp> think <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> have it bad. Look at<lb break="yes"/>
the <interp ana="#OTHER">Jews, the Irish, the Italians</interp>. <interp ana="#OTHER">They</interp><lb break="yes"/>
made it, <choice><orig>didnt</orig><reg>didn't</reg></choice> <interp ana="#PRO">they</interp>? Why <choice><orig>cant</orig><reg>can't</reg></choice> you<lb break="yes"/>
<interp ana="#AFAM">people</interp> stop making <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">bad scenes</interp></affiliation>?</p>
<p><choice><orig>Dont</orig><reg>Don't</reg></choice> <interp ana="#AFAM">your</interp> <affiliation>leaders</affiliation> have any con-<lb break="yes"/>
trol over <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> <interp ana="#ASLUR">savages</interp>? The display<lb break="yes"/>
of <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">violence</interp></affiliation> in the <orgName ref="#SGA">SGA</orgName> budget hearing
was <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">simply disgraceful</interp></affiliation>. <interp ana="#PRO">You</interp> say <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp><lb break="yes"/>
<choice><orig>dont</orig><reg>don't</reg></choice> <affiliation>want tokenism</affiliation> but <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> were<lb break="yes"/>
willing to accept only <num>two</num> <interp ana="#AFAM">black</interp> mem-<lb break="yes"/>
bers on the <orgName>cheer leading squad</orgName>.</p>
<p>Why not the whole squad? <interp ana="#PRO">You</interp> also<lb break="yes"/>
showed extreme <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">lack of respect</interp></affiliation> for<lb break="yes"/>
our <desc>great</desc> <affiliation><persName ref="#PRES">President Elkins</persName></affiliation>. <choice><orig>Hasnt</orig><reg>Hasn't</reg></choice><lb break="yes"/>
he established an effective enough<lb break="yes"/>
line of communication between <interp ana="#AFAM">you</interp><lb break="yes"/>
and <persName ref="#PRES">his administration</persName>?</p>
<p>If not, why <choice><orig>dont</orig><reg>don't</reg></choice> <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp> tell <persName ref="#PRES">him</persName> so?<lb break="yes"/>
<choice><orig>Theres</orig><reg>There's</reg></choice> a <affiliation><interp ana="#AFAM">proper way to get results</interp></affiliation><lb break="yes"/>
at the <orgName ref="#UMD">University</orgName>.</p>
<p><interp ana="#PRO">I</interp> close <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">my comments</interp></affiliation> by saying <interp ana="#PRO">you</interp><lb break="yes"/>
should take a good look at <interp ana="#AFAM">yourselves</interp><lb break="yes"/>
and realize that <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">good hard work</interp></affiliation> and a<lb break="yes"/>
<affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">good education</interp></affiliation> is all <interp ana="#AFAM">you</interp> need to get<lb break="yes"/>
ahead.</p>
<p><persName ref="#IAR"><interp ana="#CAUC">I. A. Racist</interp></persName></p>
<p><placeName><num>724</num> <interp ana="#CAUC">Reactionary</interp> Drive</placeName></p>
<p><settlement><interp ana="#CAUC">Bigot</interp></settlement>, <region>Maryland</region></p>
<p>This is a <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">letter</interp></affiliation> which is full of the<lb break="yes"/>
<affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">racism</interp></affiliation> that confronts <interp ana="#AFAM">black students</interp><lb break="yes"/>
<corr>everyday</corr>.</p>
<!--Print smudge distorts sic "b" character in "everyday"-->
<p>The <interp ana="#CAUC">person</interp> who wrote <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">this letter</interp></affiliation><lb break="yes"/>
is considered <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">armed</interp>, <interp ana="#CAUC">dangerous</interp> and<lb break="yes"/>
an <interp ana="#CAUC">enemy to America</interp></affiliation>. <interp ana="#PRO">He</interp> can be found<lb break="yes"/>
in any age group, in any establish-<lb break="yes"/>
ment, in any city or even crawling<lb break="yes"/>
out <corr>of</corr> the woodwork.</p>
<!--Print smudge distorts "f" character in "of"-->
<p><choice><orig>Wliitey</orig><reg><interp ana="#CSLUR">Whitey</interp></reg></choice>, it is <affiliation><interp ana="#CAUC">your</interp> duty</affiliation> to seek <interp ana="#CAUC">him</interp><lb break="yes"/>
out and destroy him, before <interp ana="#AFAM">we</interp> do!</p>
